(150, 2454392, 2454392, '16:30:00', '18:30:00', 'Once', 0, 'Primate Liberation Week Protest at UW Primate Research Center ', 'When: Thursday, Oct. 18th @ 4:30pm - 6:30pm&lt;br /&gt;Where: in front of Magnuson Health Science Center (1925 N.E. Pacific St.)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;In recognition of Primate Liberation Week, NARN (Northwest Animal Rights&lt;br /&gt;Network) will be holding a protest in front of the Washington National Primate&lt;br /&gt;Research Center&#039;s main facility, located in the I-Wing of the Warren G. Magnuson&lt;br /&gt;Health Sciences Center. The Infant Primate Research Laboratory (IPRL), is&lt;br /&gt;located in the RR-Wing of the same center. For this protest, we will be holding&lt;br /&gt;signs, banners &amp; handing out literature. The protest will be peaceful.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;For more information see:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.uwkillsanimals.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;www.uwkillsanimals.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Washington National Primate Research Center: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wanprc.org/WaNPRC/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.wanprc.org/WaNPRC/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Stop Animal Research Now &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.all-creatures.org/saen/wa/res-fr-wa-uws.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.all-creatures.org/saen/wa/res-fr-wa-uws.html&lt;/a&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[7X', ''),
