(152, 2454402, 2454402, '11:30:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Secret Sandwich Cafe! ', 'What: Secret Sandwich Cafe&lt;br /&gt;Why: Benefit for the Community Coalition for Environmental Justice&lt;br /&gt;When: &lt;span style=&quot;border-bottom:1pxdashedrgb(0,102,204);cursor:pointer;&quot;&gt;Sunday, October 28&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Where: Dancylvania&lt;br /&gt;           110 Harvard Ave E, between Olive and Denny   This cafe is being held as a benefit for CCEJ, the Community Coalition for Environmental Justice.  CCEJ fights for environmental and economic justice for low-income people and people of color.  For more info about their current campaigns, check out &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ccej.org/campaigns.php4&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;http://www.ccej.org/campaigns.php4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We will be serving a selection of grilled sandwiches, side dishes, beverages and desserts.  &lt;br /&gt;Your choice of a sandwich, side and non-alcoholic drink will be $10. &lt;br /&gt;Desserts, additional menu items, and boozy drinks will be available for an additional price (with nothing over $3).&lt;br /&gt;All food and drinks will be vegan and delicious.  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;As seating is limited, we are asking people to make reservations in advance.  &lt;br /&gt;We will be seating groups of 10 people at 11:30am, 1:00pm and 2:30pm.&lt;br /&gt;There will be a lounge area to hang out in before and after your lunch.  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;To make a reservation, please contact Pheonix at &lt;span style=&quot;border-bottom:1pxdashedrgb(0,102,204);cursor:pointer;&quot;&gt;(206) 293-7009&lt;/span&gt; or &lt;span style=&quot;background:transparentnonerepeatscroll0%50%;-moz-background-clip:-moz-initial;-moz-background-origin:-moz-initial;-moz-background-inline-policy:-moz-initial;&quot;&gt;mepheonix at gmail.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://colorofchange.org/jena/message.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; &