(218, 2454428, 2454428, '10:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, '&quot;FREE HUGS&quot; campaign / BUY NOTHING DAY ', 'Boycott shopping and join the fun!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date: &lt;/strong&gt;BLACK FRIDAY&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Time: &lt;/strong&gt;10 am (shoppers will be out even earlier...) until ????? &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Approx. 105th and 5th st NORTHGATE MALL in between the main mall and it&#039;s extension. Let&#039;s move into the mall, though, ok?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What: &lt;/strong&gt;Fun times engaging with xmas shoppers! Picketing:&quot;While you&#039;re shopping / bombs are dropping&quot;?, &quot;buy nothing / give something&quot;, etc, let your creativity abound! Also giving out free food (gotta counteract all that food court crap), such as baked goods and produce. If you show up, bring something with you&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Really important part: &lt;/strong&gt;This is largely a &quot;free hugs&quot; event so get ready to give hugs to anybody and everybody&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What to wear:&lt;/strong&gt; Please try to wear solid red. For at least two obvious reasons. If you don&#039;t have red, oh well.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What to bring: &lt;/strong&gt;a sign, some food, your smile and good energy, a musical instrument?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Come make your presense felt before.... &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/23/nyregion/23stores.html?_r&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Black Friday becomes Black Thursday&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Love,&lt;br /&gt;nicole&lt;br /&gt;sconicole@gmail.com ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[7X', ''),
