(345, 2454466, 2454466, '19:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'New Years Benefit @ Dog City ', 'Okay everyone, New Years eve is in just three days, so nows the time to get everyone to come to this. Send out your myspaces, emails, phone calls, whatever you prefer (there should still be some paper posters and flyers at HTFC), just get all the right people in the know. I&#039;m really excited and this is going to be really fun! Lets make sure that all the  positive, awesome people we know don&#039;t miss it eh? Thanks to everyone for their help! &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New Years Eve! Real Big!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The cause we are benefitting, in a nutshell:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Girls and women in the developing world are responsible for their families&#039; daily water needs. This means everyday, on average girls and women have to walk 5 miles and carry 5 gallons of water, which takes 5 hours of their time. &lt;br /&gt;             &lt;br /&gt; In many areas of the world, women are faced with obstacles that limits their opportunities to have a better life. They are not given equal access to education and are expected to perform hard labor, like collecting water daily. The 5 hours that is allocated to water translates into the lost opportunity for education for girls and lost economic opportunity for women. &lt;br /&gt;           &lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;           &lt;/em&gt;Issues of global poverty may seem to be beyond our personal control, but the truth is that we are in positions to help.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Music:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Yes Oh Yes&lt;/strong&gt;: Bellingham powerpop &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/yesohyes&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;  http://www.myspace.com/yesohyes&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Little Party and the Bad Business&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;The Last Slice of Butter&lt;/strong&gt; in a battle of Pop vs. Rock: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/littlepartyandbadbusiness&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; http://www.myspace.com/littlepartyandbadbusiness &lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/thelastsliceofbutter&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.myspace.com/thelastsliceofbutter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Koji Kondo&lt;/strong&gt;: pop-punk with ska chords from Texas  &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/kojikondom&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; http://www.myspace.com/kojikondom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Talbot Tagora&lt;/strong&gt;: local post-punk  &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/talbottagora&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; http://www.myspace.com/talbottagora&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Teenage Cool Kids&lt;/strong&gt;: pop-punk from texas &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/teenagecoolkids&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.myspace.com/teenagecoolkids&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Flexxx&lt;/strong&gt;: three-stage vocal assault system from Bremerton  &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/theflex&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.myspace.com/theflex&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Orcateers&lt;/strong&gt;: Local whale-core.  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dinner&lt;/strong&gt; will be Organized by Benji. anyone who wants to help him out should get in touch with him. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This Event Occurs at:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dog City: &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;4558 7th AVE NE in the U-district&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Dinner @ 7:00, Music @ 7:30&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No Alcohol &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Donations &lt;/strong&gt;for&lt;strong&gt; Global Water Projects &lt;/strong&gt;and&lt;strong&gt; Touring Bands &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;for more info:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://webuiltdogcity.blogspot.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;webuiltdogcity.blogspot.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong