(364, 2454493, 2454493, '18:30:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'BikeShack Convergence! ', 'Are you interested in being a volunteer at The BikeShack at the Wayward? Do you have an idea how to improve it, and are willing to put some time and effort into the free collective bicycle space that is the Bikeshack? Great! Then come to the first ever BikeShack Convergence. We will discuss and plan how to improve the Shack.   We&#039;re meeting at Sherwood Co-op (&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:courier;font-size:12px;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;4746 18th Ave NE in the U-District)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:courier;font-size:12px;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;   6:30 for potluck &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:courier;font-size:12px;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt;   7:00 for meeting. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:courier;font-size:12px;white-space:pre;&quot;&gt; Hope to see you there!&lt;/span&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[2X', ''),
(373, 2454534, 2454534, '19:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Art Orgy/Call to Artists/The Backpack Project ', 'Be a part of the Backpack Project&#039;s fundraiser ART ORGY, An Explosion Of Art For The Senses. In a beautiful 7000 Sq. Ft loft in Pioneer Square, this one night event will feature a fine art exhibition &amp; auction which 70% of proceeds will go to stuffing backpacks for homeless/transitional youth.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Also, included in the night will be live bands, a fashion show, indie movies, drag show/cabaret and a large dance floor with regional and national D.J.&#039;s.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; ART ORGY is the official launch of Action NorthWest&#039;s newest program, The Backpack Project.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; The Backpack Project will provide backpacks to homeless youth. These backpacks will contain clothing, food, toiletries, art supplies and a one stop shop pamphlet that outlines in detail resources regarding: LGBT health, meth issues, jobs, housing, counseling and resources for all youth. This auction will benefit the Backpack Project and proceeds will be used to stuff backpacks for homeless/transitional youth. Also, people will bring art supplies and items for the backpacks to the event. To receive a backpack at a later date homeless/transitional youth must volunteer or work with a program at one of the participating social service agencies.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;To get involved and/or donate art, email Backpack_Project@yahoo.com&lt;br /&gt;Deadline for all art is February 15. ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[8X', ''),
