(369, 2454493, 2454493, '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Monstersorri Microcinema!  Free screening! ', 'This SUNDAY come to a free screening of THE CENTURY OF THE SELF with your friends at the Monstersorri Microcinema.  THE CENTURY OF THE SELF is a powerful documentary series by the BBC and Adam Curtis, the creator of such powerful documentaries as THE POWER OF NIGHTMARES and THE TRAP.  Plus, the BBC released it into the public domain, so we won&#039;t even be acting piratey when we send you home with copies for yourself!&lt;br /&gt;&quot;This series is about how those in power have used Freud&#039;s theories to try and control the dangerous crowd in an age of mass democracy.&quot; - Adam Curtis&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;What:  7 PM - Eat Potluck&lt;br /&gt;       7:30 - The Century of the Self, Parts 1 and 2&lt;br /&gt;When:  Sunday, Jan 27th, 7-10 PM&lt;br /&gt;Where:  Monstersorri House, 2317 14th Ave S, Beacon Hill&lt;br /&gt;Cost: $0.00&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Monstersorri Microcinema is a great new experience for your minds and hearts and brains.  Two Sundays a month there will be free screenings of documentaries about free culture, carbusting and how capitalism is bad and also action movies with leftist politics at the Monsterssori House in Beacon Hill.  Also, potluck meal and potluck exchange of free mix tapes, cds and dvds! &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Free gifts for everybody!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Truly  yours,&lt;br /&gt;A. V. Flaxoil&lt;br /&gt;Global Media Fat Cat ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[8X', ''),
