(545, 2454556, 2454556, '20:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Father of the Flood, Corespondents, Thunder Grey Pilgrim, Garek Druss and Allan Davis at the Office Of Dr. Glorious ', 'Man, how is it that we keep getting such good shows? Even as I&amp;rsquo;m writing this, there are another couple in the works. Have you been coming? If not, you should be. Anyway, down to business. On Sunday, November 30th, we will be hosting the amazing Father of the Flood who comes all the way from &lt;span style=&quot;border-bottom:1pxdashedrgb(0,102,204);cursor:pointer;&quot;&gt;New Mexico&lt;/span&gt;. You can hear him at &lt;a href=&quot;http://fatheroftheflood.blogspot.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;fatheroftheflood.blogspot.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Corespondents will also be playing. They are really great and often times play with films! You can check them out at &lt;a href=&quot;http://corespondents.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Corespondents.org&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. That brings us to Thunder Grey Pilgrim. Drones and circles. Circles and drones. &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/thundergreypilgrim&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;www.myspace.com/thundergrey&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;pilgrim. Also, Garek Druss and myself will be playing. He plays as (a) story of rats and is in Dull Knife. I play as towers and am in Land What Land. We don&amp;rsquo;t even know what it is going to sound like! This should be a very very pretty night, so bring your pj&amp;rsquo;s and a pillow! ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[8X', ''),
