(535, 2454542, 2454542, '19:00:00', '21:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Monstersorri Microcinema Screening ', 'TONIGHT come watch &quot;Wild In the Streets,&quot; one of Monstersorri Microcinema&#039;s favorite films!  The tagline: &quot;If you&#039;re over thirty, you&#039;re through!&quot; a youth movement led by a super-groovy rock band and intent on lowering the voting age to 14 spreads across the US and finally overthrows the entire oldster&#039;s govmint!  A far-out cautionary tale that views like a psychedilic &quot;Animal Farm,&quot; with singing!  Also this week we will continue to enjoy selections from the &quot;illegal Art&quot; dvd collection of copyright-tenuous videos.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;What:  7 PM - Selections from &quot;Illegal Art Collection&quot;&lt;br /&gt;       8 PM - &quot;Wild In the Streets&quot; &lt;br /&gt;       *9 PM* - Get out of their house&lt;br /&gt;When:  Sunday, March 16, 7-9 PM&lt;br /&gt;Where:  Monstersorri House, 2317 14th Ave S, Beacon Hill&lt;br /&gt;Help/More Info:  206 734 4206&lt;br /&gt;Cost: $0.00&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Monstersorri Microcinema is a great new experience for your minds and hearts and brains.  Two Sundays a month there will be free screenings of documentaries about free culture, transportation, and how capitalism is bad, and also action movies with leftist politics at the Monsterssori House in Beacon Hill.  Also, bring and share mix tapes, cds and dvds!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Free gifts for everybody (if you bring them)!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Truly  yours,&lt;br /&gt;A. V. Flaxoil&lt;br /&gt;Global Media Fat Cat ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[8X', ''),
