(862, 2454667, 2454667, '00:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'YOUTH NOISE SUMMIT @ VERA PROJECT! ', '&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(27,27,22);font-family:arial;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;An event of art, activism, and community engagement&lt;br /&gt;Saturday, July 19th 2008&lt;br /&gt;Summit:  11-5pm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(27,27,22);font-family:arial;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(27,27,22);font-family:arial;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:-1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:normal;&quot;&gt;We&amp;rsquo;ll be doing lots of different activities from 11-5, from spectrograms to custom t-shirts to group project planning; but most importantly, it&amp;rsquo;s an open space to express yourself in the best way possible. We&amp;rsquo;ll be infusing the day with a variety of activities and performances. This is a chance to meet new people, and to go from the big issues to finding exactly what place you have in changing them. We&amp;rsquo;ll start the day with big picture issues involving our communities and end it with creative projects that address these problems. Get the tools to create a project that you can carry out with your peers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;MORE INFO: http://www.youthnoise.com/summit/seattle.html ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[5X', ''),
