(963, 2454702, 2454702, '12:01:00', '17:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Justice Works! grand opening ', 'Come celebrate with us!  Justice Works! is a grassroots criminal justice reform organization.  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We will hold a Grand Opening celebration with free food, a prison art show, and live entertainment.  We&#039;ll have our Set Up To Fail play, Bruce Holton - a jass pianist and poetry readings.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;For more information:  &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.justiceworks.info/&quot;&gt;www.justiceworks.info&lt;/a&gt;   206-303-7559   justice_works@yahoo.com ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[8X', ''),
(964, 2454694, 2454694, '20:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Wooden Indian Burial Ground(PDX), The Unit Breed (PDX), Sokai Stilhed, Christina Antipa/Kill Yr. Darlings and Painted Cakes (Oakland) at the Office Of Dr. Glorious ', 'Hey all,&lt;br /&gt;So, it&#039;s been kind of slow for us with the shows but we are stepping up our game with this one.   First up, you have the amazing Wooden Indian Burial Ground from Portland. (www.myspace.com/woodenindianburialground)  They played our living room once and rocked the fuck out of it.  Our living room has never quite been the same.  Dark, rockin&#039; country that I swear you will like.............................................................................&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Then, we have the Unit Breed, who also hail from our sister city of Portland.(www.myspace.com/theunitbreed)  I was once in this band for about 3 weeks and I can tell you first hand what an amazing nut Joe (songwriter/mastermind) is.  Not sure how to describe them other than using the word weird.  So, if you are weird, you will like it........................................................................&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Then there is the always amazing Sokai Stilhed.(www.myspace.com/sokaistilhed)  Heather is absolutely one of my favorite musicians and a great person to boot!  She is so good and she rarely plays out.  Ghosts, I tell you, ghosts.  She sounds like ghosts!.....................................................................................&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Then there is Christina Antipa/ Kill Yr. Darlings. (www.myspace.com/christinaantipa)  I&#039;m not that familiar with her yet but she comes highly recommended and I have been wanting to see her play for awhile.  I bet you have been wanting to see her play too.  Well, now&#039;s your chance.....................................................................................&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Then we have Painted Cakes, hailing from Oakland, California.  These fo