(1047, 2454730, 2454730, '20:00:00', '01:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Bike Porn 2&quot;bike exploitation&quot; ', 'TAKE NOTE! THE SCREENING HAS MOVED!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:130%;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Saturday, September 20th&lt;br /&gt;The Mix Lounge (aka Christoff Gallery)&lt;br /&gt;6004 12th Ave S #17&lt;br /&gt;        Seattle,     WA     98108&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.yelp.com/redir?url&quot;&gt;www.christoffgallery.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bike Porn returns to Seattle with two screenings at the F.B.K. House in Georgetown. At 8pm the infamous &lt;strong&gt;Pornography of the Bicycle&lt;/strong&gt; kicks of the night; then at 11pm the sequel, &lt;strong&gt;Bike Porn 2: Bikexploitation Recalibration &lt;/strong&gt;makes its Seattle Premiere.  Both 90-minute screenings consist of many short films from a variety of artists across North America on the theme of &quot;bike porn&quot; and &quot;bike exploitation&quot; respectively.  The movies range from the contemplative to the inventive, to the fully demonstrative.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&quot;Much of the content comes from queer filmmakers,&quot; says bicycle pornographer Reverend Phil. &quot;We have worked to try and encourage more sexual diversity in the program but really anyone who is regularly making bike porn probably does not identify as straight.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The theme for Bike Porn 3 will also be announced during the show.&lt;br /&gt;     &lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;9/20/2008&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Screenings @ 8:00 and 11:00 pm&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;F.B.K House&lt;br /&gt;6272 S Ellis&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:130%;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Mix Lounge (aka Christoff Gallery)&lt;br /&gt;6004 12th Ave S #17&lt;br /&gt;        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Georgetown, WA 98108&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://bikesmut.com&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;http://BikeSmut.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The various artists, some operating under pseudonyms, take us though a range of videos -- most of which are not available anywhere else. No DVDs of the work are available for sale; a select few works are online.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;p&gt;   This is an outdoor screening,  you may still bring a blanket, pillow or chair.&lt;/p&gt;The Cascadian Bikexploitation tour will stop in these cities:&lt;br /&gt;     9/18 Bellingham&lt;br /&gt;        9/20 Seattle&lt;br /&gt;        9/22 Olympia &lt;br /&gt;       10/2 Portland &lt;br /&gt;Please be advised of adult content&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Watch the trailer at &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;www.bikesmut.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[8X', ''),
