(1155, 2454774, 2454774, '19:00:00', '21:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'free workshop on RADICAL SUSTAINABILITY for AUTONOMOUS COMMUNITIES ', 'Mon, Nov 3rd, 7-9pm UW Thompson Hall Rm 125 --  Scott Kellogg from Rhizome Collective in Austin (http://www.rhizomecollective.org/) will be in Seattle for a short, free workshop at UW.  &lt;font&gt;&lt;font&gt;Radical Sustainability for Autonomous Communities ~  Urban Ecological Survival Skills: Exploring the Cross-Section of Permaculture and Social Activism.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Radical Sustainability:  * creating locally-based, decentralized, sustainable infrastructure in our own backyards and neighborhoods; * making simple, affordable systems from salvaged, waste &amp; recycled materials; * securing access to food, shelter, water security, waste management &amp; energy production; * emphasizing the interrelations between &#039;sustainability&#039; and class, race and international struggles for justice.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;More info:   http://www.radicalsustainability.org/    http://www.rhizomecollective.org/   &lt;br /&gt;or packrat@riseup.net&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff0000&quot; /&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff0000&quot; /&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff0000&quot; /&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[5X', '');
