(1173, 2454807, 2454807, '15:00:00', '00:01:00', 'Once', 0, 'Hollow Earth + HTFC Present: Local Label Record Craft and Zine Sale! With Lotso Bands! ', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt; 						Hollow Earth Radio and Healthy Times Fun Club are sponsoring a Holiday Local Record, Craft, and Zine Sale! December 6th at Healthy Times Fun Club in Seattle. If money is going to get spent for the holidays, why not give people an opportunity to spend it locally! &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Live Bands all Day!!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Blanket Truth&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;The Curious Mystery&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Thad Wenatchee&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Little Party and the Bad Business&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Anthony Junior&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Live bands all evening!!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Smile Brigade&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Terrordactyls&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Polka Dot Dot Dot&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Snowman Plan&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The sale is free for people to attend during the day. Once the evening show starts, we are asking for $5 donation at the door.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; We are creating this event so that we can support the local music and art communities and also raise funds to support Hollow Earth Radio. (Table fees and door donations will go to Hollow Earth Radio.) Healthy Times runs a little local store called The Closet. This will be open as well, and it benefits Seattle DIY. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;