(1235, 2454787, 2454787, '12:01:00', '14:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'The Bikery Presents A know Your RIghts Workshop ', '&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Is it illegal to ride a bike in the middle of a lane of traffic?&lt;br /&gt;* Are you supposed to signal for turns with your left or right hand?&lt;br /&gt;* What about using a crosswalk to avoid swerving through six lanes of traffic?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;These and other topics are included in our conversation-based Know Your Rights workshop, designed to allow cyclists an opportunity to share experiences, survival skills, long-unanswered questions,&lt;br /&gt; and much more. This &quot;Know Your Rights&quot; class will be followed by a community ride. If you can&#039;t make it to the class, you can meet up at the Bikery at 2pm.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.flickr.com/photos/killthewhitenoise/3025912084/&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3041/3025912084_1e22e6f7f0_o.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[2X', ''),
