(1504, 2454903, 2454903, '17:00:00', '20:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'FREE WORKSHOP: Saving Limbs: Green Spaces and Women&#039;s Lives Workshop ', '&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Where:&lt;/strong&gt; Pritchard Beach Bathhouse, 8400 55th Avenue S., Seattle, WA&lt;br /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://urbanwildernessproject.org/spacer.gif&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Dr. Williams and Dr. Kuo&#039;s groundbreaking research in Illinois proved that urban green spaces increase self-esteem and decision making for girls and reduced domestic violence which tears apart families. As Seattle&#039;s population sky rockets, we defoliate our neighborhood spaces in favor of urban density. The absence of green space may put women&#039;s lives at a greater risk. Learn what you can do to protect our social and natural Eco-systems.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://urbanwildernessproject.org/spacer.gif&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Be a part of the solution - join the R U An Endangered Species?&amp;trade; campaign to save human lives. www.urbanwildernessproject.org 206-464-8364 ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[5X', ''),
