(1507, 2454909, 2454909, '00:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Letter Writing Night @ Arctic Circle! ', '&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i471.photobucket.com/albums/rr72/seattleestateauctions/misc/temp_blah_1000.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Arctic Circle (a house in Georgetown) is hosting a letter-writing night.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We&#039;d like prisoners to know that we are here in support &amp; solidarity, whether they have been imprisoned for political reasons, the color of their skin, or some other form of bullshit. We&#039;d love it if you would stop by and join in (we are very friendly).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;8:00PM - ?:00&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;6633 Ellis Ave S&lt;br /&gt;Seattle WA 98108&lt;br /&gt;(Just a block or so down from the Squid &amp; Ink)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We&#039;ll provide the stamps, paper, and envelopes!! ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[9X', ''),
