(1983, 2455177, 2455177, '19:00:00', '00:01:00', 'Once', 0, 'Seattle Subversive Square Dance Dance ', '&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Are you letting a bad middle school dance experience effect your image of &lt;strong&gt;square dancing&lt;/strong&gt;? stop it! &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Dust off your dancing shoes and shake your tail feathers to the henhouse rounders, al pastor and the bac-o-bits. Calling by jordan ruyle, gabe strand, maggie lind, and amy hofer.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;potlucking at 7, dancing at 8&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;all ages, skill levels and peoples welcome.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;at the &lt;strong&gt;Lakeside Collective&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;11748 Lakeside Ave. NE&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Just off of the Burke Gilman, the 75, the 41, the 522, the 72 and the 65.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[3X', ''),
