(1539, 2454929, 2454929, '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'flim night @ gallery 1412 ', '&lt;font color=&quot;#7f7f00&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;flim night&lt;br /&gt;...an evening of projectable phenomena&lt;/font&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;+0&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;featuring:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;+0&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Eraserhead&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;David Lynch, usa, 1977, 89 min&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&quot;The whole film is undercurrents of sort of subconscious ... You know, and it kind of wiggles around in there, and it&#039;s how it strikes each person. It definitely means something to me, but I don&#039;t want to to talk about that. It means other things to other people, and that&#039;s great.&quot; - David Lynch&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;+0&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Frank Film&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Frank Mouris and Catherine Mouris, usa, 1973, 9 min&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&quot;Esteemed as &#039;probably the most celebrated American short,&#039; &lt;em&gt;Frank Film&lt;/em&gt; is a collection of 11,592 collages sequenced to illustrate the chronology of the filmmaker&#039;s life.  Spanning the years 1945-1973, this wildly entertaining short film goes beyond the story of one man&#039;s experience to become a collective autobiography of our time.&quot; - from the box&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;also this month, flim night continues its love affair with the work of local oddball filmmaker &lt;strong&gt;Paul Maupoux&lt;/strong&gt;, who will present a new short film whose name i don&#039;t yet know (but which will surely be sublime).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;On the first Tuesday of every month, &lt;strong&gt;Flim Night&lt;/strong&gt; showcases a variety of film-based art, with special emphasis on subversive humor, surrealism, activist and revolutionary topics, and whatever else resonates.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;donations benefit &lt;strong&gt;Seattle Food Not Bombs&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;scn.org/foodnotbombs&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;gallery 1412 &lt;br /&gt;1412 18th ave&lt;br /&gt;gallery1412.org&lt;/font&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[8X', ''),
