(1902, 2455130, 2455130, '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Report Night! ', '&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Kind of like a glorified Toast Master&amp;rsquo;s club- but way fresher!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;The plan: You research a topic of your choosing (albeit not preachy), provide some type of learning aid (visual, audio, food, etc), and present on that topic for 5-10 minute.  Some examples from other Report Nights have included:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;- A skill share on how to adjust your bike so that you don&#039;t have lower back troubles&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;- Folk musician Abner Jay (individual perform some of his sweet jams for learning aid)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;- Probiotics (learning aid yogurt)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Down for dorking out? Contact Angeli at &lt;/font&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:bhatta@u.washington.edu&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000ff&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;bhatta@u.washington.edu&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt; for more info.&lt;/font&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[9X', ''),
