(1909, 2455129, 2455129, '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Agent Green and Madison Market! ', '&lt;font color=&quot;#669900&quot;&gt;Join Agent Green to make a positive impact on our community, have a great time, and meet wonderful people!&lt;/font&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We need you to shop for groceries!&lt;em&gt; Agent Green is an organized mob that helps local businesses live their values.  Our next mission is to help the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.madisonmarket.com/&quot;&gt;Central Co-op&#039;s Madison Market&lt;/a&gt; go green.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;On October 24, 25% of all sales at the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.madisonmarket.com/&quot;&gt;Central Co-op&#039;s Madison Market&lt;/a&gt; will be dedicated to energy efficient retrofits and other improvements to make the store a more environmentally-friendly place to shop. Our purchasing power, combined with the Seattle City Light&amp;rsquo;s cash rebates for energy efficient upgrades, will create the capital and inertia needed to aid &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.madisonmarket.com/&quot;&gt;Central Co-op&#039;s Madison Market&lt;/a&gt; in drastically reducing its energy use.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This won&amp;rsquo;t be your typical day of shopping. The Agent Green team will be at the store from 10:00am-2:00pm. There will be food vendors present and Slow Skate will be performing in the store from 12:00-1:00pm. We will be accepting food donations for Northwest Harvest at the event. Any time during the day you can take your Central Co-op receipt over to &lt;a href=&quot;http://bluebirdseattle.blogspot.com/&quot;&gt;Bluebird Ice Cream&lt;/a&gt; and you will get a free second scoop with the purchase of your first scoop.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In appreciation for joining the cause &lt;a href=&quot;http://bluebirdseattle.blogspot.com/&quot;&gt;Bluebird Ice Cream&lt;/a&gt; will be hosting a private party complete with drinks and a live band.  Your Central Co-op receipt is your ticket to the 