(2006, 2455255, 2455255, '00:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Benefit for Seattle Solidarity Network ', '&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.dodiy.org/feb27benefit_web400px.jpg&quot; /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Saturday, February 27, there will be a benefit show for the Seattle Solidarity Network.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Seattle Solidarity is a volunteer network of working people who believe in standing up for our rights. Our goal is to support our fellow workers&#039; strikes and struggles, build solidarity, and organize to deal with specific job, housing, and other problems caused by the greed of the rich and powerful.  Learn more about them at &lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://www.seasol.net/&quot;&gt;www.seasol.net&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;@ The Big House&lt;br /&gt; which is somewhere in Capitol Hill.&lt;br /&gt; Email bighouse@dodiy.org and we&#039;ll send you the exact address.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Music by:&lt;br /&gt; MEGABOG&lt;br /&gt; WET PAINT&lt;br /&gt; JOE MARTIN&lt;br /&gt; THE GREATEST PLACE TO&lt;br /&gt; THOUSANDS&lt;br /&gt;(The Pica Beats CANCELLED)&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Everything starts at 8:00PM.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; $8 at the door, goes directly to the Seattle Solidarity Network.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;NOTE FOR EVERYONE: Everyone will enter through the back door &amp; it is wheelchair accessible. Only the basement (where most of the music will happen) is wheelchair accessible. Please be kind to people with chemical &amp; scent sensitivies &amp;ndash; Please Don&amp;rsquo;t Wear Scented Deodorant or Perfumes &amp; Don&amp;rsquo;t Smoke Near The Non-Smokers. We&amp;rsquo;re trying to make this event accessible to as many people as we can, so please send an email to bighouse@dodiy.org if you need any accommodations. Also Read This: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scn.org/activism/calendar/disabilities.html&quot;&gt;www.scn.org/activism/calendar/disabilities.html&lt;/a&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[3X', ''),
