(2090, 2455282, 2455282, '18:30:00', '21:30:00', 'Once', 0, 'Report Night March 26! ', '&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Hi Everyone, &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;It&#039;s time again for Report Night, this month on March 26 starting at 6:30 at my place, 936 20th Ave. When you arrive, go up onto the porch and through the door on the LEFT.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Of course the basic premise of Report Night is that you pick a topic of your choosing, have some type of learning aid to go with it (visual, audio, food, etc) and then you spend 5-10 minutes presenting on it. And really it can be anything. &lt;/font&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Check out our blog at: &lt;/font&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://seattlereportnight.blogspot.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000ff&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;http://seattlereportnight.blogspot.com/&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;If interested in reporting shoot me an e-mail back so I can add you to the list.&lt;/font&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;I usually write here that &quot;you can&#039;t come if you&#039;re an asshole.&quot; And yes, please keep the ass-holery at home, but also we trying to promote a Safer Space (i.e. checking racist, homophobic, sexist, etc. comments) while also assuming positive intent. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Shoot an e-mail back for the head count, and feel free to pass the word along to anyone who&#039;d be interested.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Cheers!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Rebecca&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:rebecca.nur@gmail.com&quot;&gt;rebecca.nur@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/font&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[9X', ''),
(2091, 2455304, 2455304, '21:30:00', '22:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'The Mountain Goats: Life of the World to Come ', '&lt;p&gt;(Rian Johnson, USA, 2010, Digi-Beta, 60 min)&lt;/p&gt; 	 		 	                         					 					 					 					 						 	                                        	 		 			 		 				&lt;p&gt;Co-presented by &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.easystreetonline.com/&quot;&gt;Easy  Street Records&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exclusive door prizes to be raffled off before the show, including  a signed copy of the upcoming limited-edition DVD!&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt; 		 		 			 		 	             					 					 					 					  					 					 					 					&lt;p&gt; 						 							Saturday, Apr 17 at 09:30PM&lt;br /&gt; 						&lt;/p&gt; 					 					 					 	                                 	 		 	  &lt;p&gt;Join us for the DVD release of this documentary about The Mountain  Goats frontman John Darnielle as he returns to Pomona College&amp;mdash;where he  performed Bach minuets as an 8-year-old piano student&amp;mdash;in &lt;em&gt;The Life Of  The World To Come,&lt;/em&gt; playing last year&#039;s Bible-based concept record  of the same name in solo and duet performances. Filmed by Rian Johnson (&lt;em&gt;Brick,  The Brothers Bloom&lt;/em&gt;), &lt;em&gt;Life Of The World To Come &lt;/em&gt;shows  Darnielle in his usual live element, stripping his  confessionals/narratives until there&#039;s nothing left but his defiant  nasally voice and minimal accompaniment on vocals by Rachel from the  Bright Mountain Choir.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s a simple, unfussy document of one of our greatest living  songwriters wrestling with his faith through gorgeous music.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In honor of World Record Store Day, &lt;em&gt;Life of the World to Come &lt;/em&gt;will  be available for sale on DVD on April 17 &lt;strong&gt;only&lt;/strong&gt;.  Find  out more at &lt;a href=&quot;http://recordstoreday.com/&quot;&gt;www.recordstoreday.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt; Get tickets: http://nwfilmforum.org/live/page/calendar/1302 &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;  &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?v&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://s7.addthis.com/static/btn/v2/lg-addthis-en.gif&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;file:///Users/publicitydirector/Library/Caches/TemporaryItems/moz-screenshot.png&quot; /&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[8X', '');
