(2143, 2455289, 2455289, '00:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'MICROCOSM TOUR 2010! AT LEFT BANK BOOKS! ', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://ediblesecrets.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/microtour.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;COME CHECK OUT MICROCOSM TOUR 2010!! &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;They&#039;ve got some of the raddest &#039;zines in your collection, and this Friday, they&#039;ll be in Seattle to answer any questions  you may have about their project, as well as showcase a couple awesome performances in our humble little bookshop! The event is FREE!! &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There will be a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff0000&quot;&gt;COOKING SHOW &amp; FREE VEGAN SNACKS!&lt;/font&gt; w/ Josh Ploeg, author of In Search of the Lost Taste! There will be a &lt;font color=&quot;#cc66cc&quot;&gt;DIY FILMSCREENING OF &quot;IF IT AIN&#039;T CHEAP IT AIN&#039;T PUNK&quot;&lt;/font&gt; with Microcosm founder Joe Biel!! There will be a &lt;font color=&quot;#33cc00&quot;&gt;TOURING&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font color=&quot;#33cc00&quot;&gt;MUSEUM SHOWCASING THE SECRET HISTORY OF FOOD &amp; ESPIONAGE&lt;/font&gt;!!!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Friday, April 2nd, @ 7:30PM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Left Bank Books&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;92 Pike St.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;(Corner of 1st &amp; Pike! Next to the flower shop!)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[9X', ''),
