(2162, 2455310, 2455310, '00:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Spring into Bed Benefit! Nettle Honey, Junk Bones ', 'On Friday April 23rd, the P-Patch house is hosting an awesome benefit show and secret cafe to raise money for Spring Into Bed!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;whats IS it?&lt;br /&gt;Spring into Bed is both a celebration of urban gardening and sustainable food systems as well as a social justice project that hopes to raise enough money to build gardens for 10 low income families across Seattle!&lt;br /&gt;more info here: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.springintobed.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#3b5998&quot;&gt;http://www.springintobed.org/&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;at 6PM we will be hosting a secret cafe, come eat and drink delicious home-cooked local, organic, vegan and vegetarian food; all the money raised will go to SIB.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;at 9PM there will be an &quot;after party&quot; with some fun tunes to dance to:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nettle Honey (Seattle)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/nettlehoney&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#3b5998&quot;&gt;http://www.myspace.com/nettlehoney&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Junk Bones (Seattle)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/junkbones&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#3b5998&quot;&gt;http://www.myspace.com/junkbones&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;for the cafe, please bring $10; or for the after party, please bring $5. remember this is a BENEFIT.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We hope to see you there! invite yer friends! ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[8X', ''),
(2163, 2455310, 2455310, '19:30:00', '00:01:00', 'Once', 0, 'Tranny Roadshow! ', 'Lakeside Collective is hosting the Tranny Roadshow&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;11748 Lakeside Ave NE&lt;br /&gt;Seattle, WA 98125&lt;br /&gt;lakesidecollective@gmail.com&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Tranny Roadshow is a multimedia performance art extravaganza. It is  composed of an eclectic group of artists, each one self-identified as  transgender, and includes poets, rappers, filmmakers, storytellers,  breakdancers, rock bands, comedians, actors, folk singers,  photographers, zinesters, and more. Stationary art (i.e. photography and  sculpture) is displayed, but most of the presentation is the live show,  a unique variety show where the expression of gender and the expression  of self are inseparable. The show is a fluid entity, changing to suit  the artists and the crowd, but always it is full of intelligence, fun  and humor.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Although the Tranny Roadshow is done entirely by  transpeople, it is not exclusively for transpeople. It is a raucous  evening of entertainment, open and accessible to people of all  backgrounds. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Suggested donation: $5-10. (No one turned away!)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;All  Ages&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;DANCE PARTY to follow!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;**We try to make our home a  safe(r) space for all by minimizing the presence of transphobia, racism,  ableism, sexism, sizeism, ageism, homophobia, and other forms of  oppression.**&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Our home is wheelchair accessible. However, our  driveway is quite steep and not safe for most vehicles. We can assist  down the driveway in one of our vehicles, just let us know. ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[3X', ''),
(2164, 2455320, 2455320, '00:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'UW Campus Strike--Pickets and a Picnic ', '&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&#039;lucidagrande&#039;,tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;border-collapse:collapse;color:rgb(51,51,51);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border-collapse:separate;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:small;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Picket lines &lt;/strong&gt;all day at 15th Ave NE and NE 40th St, beginning at 8AM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;style&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:small;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Picnic with the picketers&lt;/strong&gt; at 11 AM, same location.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;style&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:small;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ALL ARE WELCOME!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;style&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:small;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;style&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:small;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;We did not create this crisis.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;  &lt;/strong&gt;We should not pay for it by sacrificing our education, job security, wages, and health.  In solidarity with teaching and research assistants, undergraduates and graduate students, custodians and state workers, and the struggle for immigrant rights--STRIKE.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;style&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;style&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:small;&quot;&gt;for more info., see &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;style&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:small;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://nobudgetcutsuw.blogspot.com/&quot;&gt;nobudgetcutsuw.blogspot.com/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&qu