(2185, 2455367, 2455367, '18:00:00', '20:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Kick Some Apathy Kickball Tournament ', 'This is the first annual kickball tournament to benefit People For Puget  Sound. Participants will be in a winner- takes-all-bragging-rights  kickball tourney to help save our Sound!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Spectators will be  enjoying the view of 45 amateur kickball players running around the  field and attempting to live out their dreams of being Pele.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Players  must be 18+;  spectators of all ages welcome!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;$25-$40  registration fee to play, fan tickets $10 (remember, this is a benefit  fundraiser!)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bring you water bottle, a winning spirit, and money  to donate to a GREAT cause!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;There will be a live auction for  team-captain, so bring a checkbook or credit card. Be sure to register  EARLY! The longer you wait the higher the registration fee. Only 45  player spots available!  There will also be an opportunity (for a  donation) to name the other team!&lt;br /&gt;To Register: Contact Cole Reese at  creese@pugetsound.org OR go to &lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://pugetsound.org/connect/events/061910kick/&quot;&gt;http://pugetsound.org/connect/events/061910kick/&lt;/a&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[9X', ''),
