(2192, 2455338, 2455338, '20:00:00', '00:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Older Blood and Jacob Wick and Friends at gallery 1412 (1412 18th ave. at union) ', 'hey out there!&lt;br /&gt;so, this friday there is a really great show taking place at gallery 1412 with&lt;br /&gt;older blood and jacob wick and friends.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;older blood is heather cullen (sokai stilhed) and allan davis (from land what land).&lt;br /&gt;old, old, ancient, old country blues and mountain ballads poured out into the ether&lt;br /&gt;and channeled back to earth.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;jacob wick and friends is jacob wick, wilson shook and gust burns.  experimental,&lt;br /&gt;improvisational sounds for trumpet, sax, piano and others.  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;you should come! ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[3X', ''),
(2193, 2455345, 2455345, '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 'Once', 0, 'Slow Teeth, Matador, Tin Tree Factory &amp; Junk Bones @ The P-Patch! ', '&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:&#039;lucidagrande&#039;;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;its folklife! its friday night! lets have a show!&lt;br /&gt;come out to the P-Patch for an amazing show with....&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Slow Teeth (portland)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/slowteeth&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.myspace.com/slowteeth&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Matador (santa cruz)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/matadorfromsantacruz&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.myspace.com/matadorfromsantacruz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Tin Tree Factory (olympia)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/tintreefactory&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.myspace.com/tintreefactory&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Junk Bones (seattle)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.myspace.com/junkbones&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.myspace.com/junkbones&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:&#039;lucidagrande&#039;;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:&#039;lucidagrande&#039;;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;show starts at 7pm!  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:&#039;lucidagrande&#039;;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;the P-Patch is located at 4030 7th ave NE in the U-Dist&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:&#039;lucidagrande&#039;;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;a donation is requested for the touring bands, but NO ONE TURNED AWAY FOR LACK OF FUNDS.&lt;br /&gt;invite yer friends!&lt;/span&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[3X', ''),
(2194, 2455353, 2455353, '18:00:00', '00:01:00', 'Once', 0, 'United States Social Forum Benefit! ', 'Common Action is hosting a benefit on Saturday June 5th for the 2nd U.S. Social Forum to be held this June 22-26th in Detroit Michigan. (www.ussf2010.org) at &lt;strong&gt;The Lakeside Collective (11748 Lakeside Ave. NE off of Sandpoint and 123rd) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The US Social Forum will provide a space to build relationships, learn from each other&#039;s experiences, and share analysis of the problems our communities face. It will help develop leadership, vision, and strategy needed to realize another world.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Another World is Possible! Another US is Necessary!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Come help the NW represent ourselves! &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Common Action (www.&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://www.nwcommonaction.org/&quot;&gt;http://www.nwcommonaction.org/&lt;/a&gt;) along with The Lakeside Collective will host this night of food, music, dancing, friends, and solidarity. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Schedule:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;6-8 PM Secret Cafe $10.00 (Dinner includes salad, entree, and desert) *Vegan and vegetarian options are available. **Wine available for $5.00 or donation &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;8-9 PM Show with Corespondents and Gene Pool &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;9 PM -Late Dance Party $5.00 or donation for entry/Beer and wine $5.00 or donation (There will be a keg!)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Spread the word!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://hphotos-snc3.fbcdn.net/hs319.snc3/28592_517827388424_82300255_30711312_1224039_n.jpg&quot; /&gt; ', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '0[4X', ''),
